"準備の詳細については、xref:administration:live-patching-channel-setup.adoc[]"
"を参照してください。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/live-patching-sles12.adoc:11
#: modules/administration/pages/live-patching-sles15.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Setting up for Live Patching"
