#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/live-patching-sles12.adoc:12
msgid ""
"Select the client you want to manage with Live Patching from menu:"
"Systems[Overview], and on the system details page navigate to the menu:"
"Software[Packages > Install] tab."
