"| SLES | openscap-utils | scap-security-guide\n"
"| openSUSE | openscap-utils | scap-security-guide\n"
"| RHEL | openscap-utils | scap-security-guide-redhat\n"
"| CentOS | openscap-utils | scap-security-guide-redhat\n"
