"Thu Jun  3 15:18:49 2021 - DEBUG | shell triggers finished successfully\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:10
msgid ""
"The transfer amount was roughly 1.8 GB.  The transfer took almost 30 minutes."
msgstr "転送量は約1.8GBでした。  転送には30分ほどかかりました。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:11
