"A script to accomplish this task is available for download at https://suse."
"my.salesforce.com/sfc/p/1i000000gLOd/a/1i000000ll5B/"
"B2AmvIJN2_JsAyjTQzCVP_x5ioVgd0bYN9X9NpMugS8."
