#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:28
msgid ""
"Adjust ethX to the respective network interface {productname} uses to "
"communicate with the proxy."
msgstr ""
"プロキシと通信するために{productname}が使用する各ネットワークインターフェイス"
"にehtXを調整します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:29
msgid ""
"At last, ssh communication will not be captured to reduce the number of "
"packages even further."
msgstr ""
"最後に、さらにパッケージ数を削減するため、ssh通信はキャプチャされません。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:30
msgid "Start a cobbler sync."
msgstr "cobbler syncを開始します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:31
msgid ""
"To force a sync, delete the cobbler json cache file first and then issue "
"cobbler sync:"
msgstr ""
"同期を強化するため、最初にcobbler jsonキャッシュファイルを削除してから、 "
"cobbler syncを発行します。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:32
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"rm /var/lib/cobbler/pxe_cache.json\n"
"cobbler sync\n"
msgstr ""
"rm /var/lib/cobbler/pxe_cache.json\n"
"cobbler sync\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:33
msgid "When cobbler is finished, stop the TCPdumps."
msgstr "cobblerが終了したら、 TCPdumpsを停止します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:34
msgid ""
"Open the TCPdumps using Wireshark, go to [guimenu]``Statistics > "
"Conversations`` and wait for the dump to be analyzed."
msgstr ""
"Wiresharkを使用してTCPdumpsを開き、［[guimenu]``Statistics（統計） > "
"Conversations（対話）``］に移動して、ダンプが分析されるのを待ちます。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:35
msgid ""
"Switch to the TCP tab.  The number shown on this tab gives the total number "
"of conversations captured between SUSE Manager and SUSE Manager Proxy."
msgstr ""
"TCPタブに切り替えます。  このタブに表示される数は、SUSE ManagerとSUSE "
"Manager Proxy間でキャプチャされた合計対話数を示しています。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:36
msgid "Look for the column [guimenu]``Duration``."
msgstr "［[guimenu]``Duration``］（期間）列を探します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:37
msgid ""
"Start by sorting in ascending order to find out the minimal amount of time "
"it took to transfer a file."
msgstr "昇順にソートして開始し、ファイルの転送にかかった最小時間を確認します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:38
msgid ""
"Continue by sorting in descending order to find out the maximum values for "
"the big files, for example kernel and initrd transfers."
msgstr ""
"降順にソートして続行し、カーネルやinitrdの転送など、大きなファイルの最大値を"
"確認します。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:39
msgid "Ignore ports 4505 and 4506 as these are used for Salt communication."
msgstr "ポート4505と4506はSalt通信に使用されるため無視してください。"

#. === Conclusion 
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:40
msgid ""
"Analysis of the TCPdumps showed the transfer of small files with a size of "
"approx. 1800 bytes from {productname} Server to Proxy took around 0.3 "
"seconds."
msgstr ""
"TCPdumpsの分析では、{productname}サーバからプロキシへの、サイズが約1800バイト"
"の小さなファイルの転送に約0.3秒かかったことを示しています。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:41
msgid ""
"While there were not many big files, the high number of smaller files "
"resulted high number of established connections as new TCP connection is "
"created for every single transferred file."
msgstr ""
"大きなファイルは多くありませんでしたが、小さなファイルの数が多いため、転送さ"
"れるファイルごとに新しいTCP接続が作成され、確立された接続数が多くなりました。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-highsynctimesoverwan.adoc:42
msgid ""
"Therefore, knowing the minimal amount of transfer time and a number of "
"connections needed (approx. 5000 in the example), gives an approximate "
"estimated time for the overall transfer time: 5000 * 0.3 / 60 = 25 minutes."
msgstr ""
"したがって、最小転送時間と必要な接続数(たとえば、約5000)がわかれば、転送時間"
"全体の概算推定時間が得られます(5000 * 0.3 / 60 = 25分)。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Renaming {productname} Server"
msgstr "{productname}サーバの名前変更のトラブルシューティング"

#
#
#
#
#. PUT THIS COMMENT AT THE TOP OF TROUBLESHOOTING SECTIONS
#. Troubleshooting format:
#. One sentence each:
#. Cause: What created the problem?
#. Consequence: What does the user see when this happens?
#. Fix: What can the user do to fix this problem?
#. Result: What happens after the user has completed the fix?
#. If more detailed instructions are required, put them in a "Resolving" procedure:
#. .Procedure: Resolving Widget Wobbles
#. . First step
#. . Another step
#. . Last step
#. Showing my working. --LKB 2020-06-22
#. Cause: Renaming the hostname
#. Consequence: Changes not picked up by db, clients and proxies
#. Fix: Use the [command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename`` script to update the settings in the PostgreSQL database and the internal structures of {productname}.
#. Result: Renaming is successfully propagated
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:2
msgid ""
"If you change the hostname of the {productname} Server locally, your "
"{productname} installation ceases to work properly.  This is because the "
"changes have not been made in the database, which prevents the changes from "
"propagating out your clients and any proxies."
msgstr ""
"{productname}サーバのホスト名をローカルで変更する場合は、{productname}インス"
"トールが適切に機能しなくなります。  これは、変更がデータベースで行われていな"
"いため、変更がクライアントとプロキシに伝播されないためです。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:3
msgid ""
"If you need to change the hostname of the {productname} Server, you can do "
"so using the [command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename`` script.  This script "
"updates the settings in the PostgreSQL database and the internal structures "
"of {productname}."
msgstr ""
"{productname}サーバのホスト名を変更する必要がある場合は、"
"[command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename``スクリプトを使用して変更できます。  こ"
"のスクリプトはPostgreSQLデータベースの設定と{productname}の内部構造を更新しま"
"す。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:4
msgid ""
"The [command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename`` script is part of the "
"[package]``spacewalk-utils`` package."
msgstr ""
"[command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename``スクリプトは[package]``spacewalk-"
"utils``パッケージの一部です。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:5
msgid ""
"The only mandatory parameter for the script is the newly configured IP "
"address of the {productname} Server."
msgstr ""
"このスクリプトの唯一の必須パラメータは{productname}サーバの新たに設定されたIP"
"アドレスです。"

#. type: Block title
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Procedure: Renaming {productname} Server"
msgstr "プロシージャ: {productname}サーバの名前変更"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:7
msgid ""
"Change the network settings of the server on the system level locally and "
"remotely at the DNS server."
msgstr ""
"システムレベルのサーバのネットワーク設定を、DNSサーバでローカルおよびリモート"
"で変更します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:8
msgid ""
"You also need to provide configuration settings for reverse name "
"resolution.  Changing network settings is done in the same way as with "
"renaming any other system."
msgstr ""
"逆引き名前解決のための設定を指定する必要もあります。  ネットワーク設定の変更"
"は、他のシステムの名前変更と同じ方法で実行されます。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:9
msgid ""
"Reboot the {productname} Server to use the new network configuration and to "
"ensure the hostname has changed."
msgstr ""
"{productname}サーバを再起動して、新しいネットワーク構成を使用し、ホスト名が変"
"更されていることを確認します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:10
msgid ""
"Run the script [command]``spacewalk-hostname-rename`` script with the public "
"IP address of the server."
msgstr ""
"サーバのパブリックIPアドレスを使用して、[command]``spacewalk-hostname-"
"rename``スクリプトを実行します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:11
msgid ""
"If the server is not using the new hostname, the script fails.  Be aware "
"that this script refreshes the pillar data for all Salt minion: the time it "
"takes to run depends on the number of registered Salt systems."
msgstr ""
"サーバが新しいホスト名を使用していない場合、スクリプトは失敗します。  このス"
"クリプトがすべてのSalt minionのpillarデータを更新することに注意してください。"
"実行にかかる時間は登録済みSaltシステムの数によって異なります。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:12
msgid ""
"Re-configure your clients to make your environment aware of the new hostname "
"and IP address."
msgstr ""
"クライアントを再設定して、環境に新しいホスト名とIPアドレスを認識させるように"
"します。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:13
msgid ""
"In the Salt minion configuration file [path]``/etc/salt/minion``, you must "
"specify the name of the new Salt master ({productname} Server):"
msgstr ""
"Salt minion設定ファイルの[path]``/etc/salt/minion``で、新しいSaltマスター"
"({productname}サーバ)の名前を指定する必要があります。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:14
#, no-wrap
msgid "master: <new_hostname>\n"
msgstr "master: <new_hostname>\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:15
msgid "Once this is changed, restart the [literal]``salt-minion` process:"
msgstr "これが変更されたら、[literal]``salt-minion``プロセスを再起動します。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:16
#, no-wrap
msgid "systemctl restart salt-minion\n"
msgstr "systemctl restart salt-minion\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:17
msgid ""
"To fully propagate the hostname to the minion configuration apply the high "
"state.  Applying the high state will update the hostname in the repository "
"URLs."
msgstr ""
"ホスト名がminion設定に完全に伝播されるようにするには、highstateを適用しま"
"す。  highstateを適用すると、リポジトリURLのホスト名が更新されます。"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:18
msgid ""
"Traditional clients have the [path]``/etc/sysconfig/rhn/up2date`` "
"configuration file that must be changed.  With a re-activation key you can "
"re-register traditional clients (if there are any).  For more information, "
"see xref:client-configuration:registration-cli.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"従来のクライアントには、変更される必要がある[path]``/etc/sysconfig/rhn/"
"up2date``設定ファイルがあります。  再アクティベーションキーを使用すると、従来"
"のクライアント(存在する場合)を再登録できます。  詳細については、xref:client-"
"configuration:registration-cli.adoc[]を参照してください。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-hostname-rename.adoc:19
msgid ""
"If you use PXE boot through a proxy, you must check the configuration "
"settings of the proxy.  On the proxy, run the [command]``configure-tftpsync."
"sh`` setup script and enter the requested information.  For more "
"information, see xref:installation-and-upgrade:proxy-setup.adoc[]."
