#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Synchronization"
msgstr "同期のトラブルシューティング"

#
#
#
#. PUT THIS COMMENT AT THE TOP OF TROUBLESHOOTING SECTIONS
#. Troubleshooting format:
#. One sentence each:
#. Cause: What created the problem?
#. Consequence: What does the user see when this happens?
#. Fix: What can the user do to fix this problem?
#. Result: What happens after the user has completed the fix?
#. If more detailed instructions are required, put them in a "Resolving" procedure:
#. .Procedure: Resolving Widget Wobbles
#. . First step
#. . Another step
#. . Last step
#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:2
msgid ""
"Synchronization can fail for a number of reasons.  To get more information "
"about a connection problem, run this command:"
msgstr ""
"同期はさまざまな理由で失敗する可能性があります。  接続問題に関する詳細情報を"
"取得するには、次のコマンドを実行します。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:3
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"export URLGRABBER_DEBUG=DEBUG\n"
"spacewalk-repo-sync -c <channelname> <options> > /var/log/spacewalk-repo-sync-$(date +%F-%R).log 2>&1\n"
msgstr ""
"export URLGRABBER_DEBUG=DEBUG\n"
"spacewalk-repo-sync -c <channelname> <options> > /var/log/spacewalk-repo-sync-$(date +%F-%R).log 2>&1\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:4
msgid ""
"You can also check logs created by Zypper at [path]``/var/log/zypper.log``"
msgstr ""
"[path]``/var/log/zypper.log``にあるZypperによって作成されたログを確認すること"
"もできます。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:5
#, no-wrap
msgid "GPG Key Mismatch"
msgstr "GPGキーの不一致"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:6
msgid ""
"{productname} does not automatically trust third party GPG keys.  If package "
"synchronization fails, it could be because of an untrusted GPG key.  You can "
"find out if this is the case by opening [path]``/var/log/rhn/reposync`` and "
"looking for an error like this:"
msgstr ""
"{productname}はサードパーティのGPGキーを自動的に信頼しません。  パッケージ同"
"期が失敗する場合は、信頼されていないGPGキーが原因である可能性があります。  こ"
"の場合は、[path]``/var/log/rhn/reposync``を開いて、次のようなエラーを検索する"
"ことで確認できます。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:7
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"['/usr/bin/spacewalk-repo-sync', '--channel', 'sle-12-sp1-ga-desktop-\n"
"nvidia-driver-x86_64', '--type', 'yum', '--non-interactive']\n"
"RepoMDError: Cannot access repository. Maybe repository GPG keys are not imported\n"
msgstr ""
"['/usr/bin/spacewalk-repo-sync', '--channel', 'sle-12-sp1-ga-desktop-\n"
"nvidia-driver-x86_64', '--type', 'yum', '--non-interactive']\n"
"RepoMDError: Cannot access repository. Maybe repository GPG keys are not imported\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:8
msgid ""
"To resolve the problem, you need to import the GPG key to {productname}.  "
"For more on importing GPG keys, see xref:administration:repo-metadata.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
"この問題を解決するには、{productname}にGPGキーをインポートする必要がありま"
"す。  GPGキーのインポートの詳細については、xref:administration:repo-metadata."
"adoc[]を参照してください。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:9
#, no-wrap
msgid "GPG Key Removal from [literal]``spacewalk-repo-sync``"
msgstr "[literal]``spacewalk-repo-sync``からのGPGキーの削除"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:10
msgid ""
"When a GPG key for repository has been manually imported using "
"[literal]``spacewalk-repo-sync``, and this key is no longer needed (for "
"example if the the key was compromised, or was used for testing purposes "
"only), it can be removed from the zypper RPM database used by "
"[literal]``spacewalk-repo-sync`` with the following command:"
msgstr ""
"リポジトリのGPGキー が[literal]``spacewalk-repo-sync``を使用して手動でイン"
"ポートされ、このキーが不要になった場合(たとえば、キーが侵害された場合や、テス"
"ト目的専用で使用された場合)、次のコマンドを使用して、[literal]``spacewalk-"
"repo-sync``によって使用されるzypper RPMデータベースから削除できます。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:11
#, no-wrap
msgid "rpm --dbpath=/var/lib/spacewalk/reposync/root/var/lib/rpm/ -e gpg-pubkey-*\n"
msgstr "rpm --dbpath=/var/lib/spacewalk/reposync/root/var/lib/rpm/ -e gpg-pubkey-*\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:12
msgid ""
"where [literal]``gpg-pubkey-*`` is the name of the GPG key to be removed."
msgstr "ここで、[literal]``gpg-pubkey-*``は削除されるGPGキーの名前です。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:13
#, no-wrap
msgid "Renewing GPG Key"
msgstr "GPGキーの更新"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:14
msgid ""
"If you want to renew a GPG key, first remove the old key, and then generate "
"and import a new one."
msgstr ""
"GPGキーを更新する場合は、まず古いキーを削除してから、新しいキーを生成してイン"
"ポートします。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:15
#, no-wrap
msgid "Checksum Mismatch"
msgstr "チェックサムの不一致"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:16
msgid ""
"If a checksum has failed, you might see an error like this in the [path]``/"
"var/log/rhn/reposync/*.log`` log file:"
msgstr ""
"チェックサムが失敗すると、[path]``/var/log/rhn/reposync/*.log``ログファイルに"
"次のようなエラーが表示される場合があります。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:17
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"Repo Sync Errors: (50, u'checksums did not match\n"
"326a904c2fbd7a0e20033c87fc84ebba6b24d937 vs\n"
"afd8c60d7908b2b0e2d95ad0b333920aea9892eb', 'Invalid information uploaded\n"
"to the server')\n"
"The package microcode_ctl-1.17-102.57.62.1.x86_64 which is referenced by\n"
"patch microcode_ctl-8413 was not found in the database. This patch has\n"
"been skipped.\n"
msgstr ""
"Repo Sync Errors: (50, u'checksums did not match\n"
"326a904c2fbd7a0e20033c87fc84ebba6b24d937 vs\n"
"afd8c60d7908b2b0e2d95ad0b333920aea9892eb', 'Invalid information uploaded\n"
"to the server')\n"
"The package microcode_ctl-1.17-102.57.62.1.x86_64 which is referenced by\n"
"patch microcode_ctl-8413 was not found in the database. This patch has\n"
"been skipped.\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:18
msgid ""
"You can resolve this error by running the synchronization from the command "
"prompt with the [command]``-Y`` option:"
msgstr ""
"[command]``-Y``オプションを使用して、コマンドラインプロンプトから同期を実行す"
"ることで、このエラーを解決できます。"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:19
#, no-wrap
msgid "spacewalk-repo-sync --channel <channelname> -Y\n"
msgstr "spacewalk-repo-sync --channel <channelname> -Y\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:20
msgid ""
"This option verifies the repository data before the synchronization, rather "
"than relying on locally cached checksums."
msgstr ""
"このオプションはローカルにキャッシュされたチェックサムに依存するのではなく、"
"同期前にリポジトリデータを検証します。"

#. type: Labeled list
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:21
#, no-wrap
msgid "Connection Timeout"
msgstr "接続タイムアウト"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:22
msgid "If the download times out with the following error:"
msgstr "ダウンロードが次のエラーでタイムアウトする場合:"

#. type: delimited block -
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:23
#, no-wrap
msgid "28, 'Operation too slow. Less than 1000 bytes/sec transferred the last 300 seconds\n"
msgstr "28, 'Operation too slow. Less than 1000 bytes/sec transferred the last 300 seconds\n"

#. type: Plain text
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-sync.adoc:24
msgid ""
"You can resolve this error by specifying [literal]``reposync_timeout`` and "
"[literal]``reposync_minrate`` configuration values in [path]``/etc/rhn/rhn."
"conf``.  By default, when less than 1000 bytes per second are transferred in "
"300 secs, the download is aborted.  You can adjust the number of bytes per "
"second with [literal]``reposync_minrate``, and the number of seconds to wait "
"with [literal]``reposync_timeout``."
msgstr ""
"このエラーは、[path]``/etc/rhn/rhn.conf``で[literal]``reposync_timeout``と"
"[literal]``reposync_minrate``の設定値を指定することで解決できます。  デフォル"
"トでは、300秒で1秒あたり1000バイト未満の転送が行われると、ダウンロードが中止"
"されます。  [literal]``reposync_minrate``で1秒あたりのバイト数を調整でき、"
"[literal]``reposync_timeout``で待機する秒数を調整できます。"

#. type: Title =
#: modules/administration/pages/troubleshooting/tshoot-taskomatic.adoc:1
#, no-wrap
msgid "Troubleshooting Taskomatic"
msgstr "Taskomaticのトラブルシューティング"

